    "body": "Multiline editing is a very nice feature.  As a longtime vim and bash user, though, the switch to IPython 5.x and prompt_toolkit has been jarring.  I would much prefer that vi-mode in prompt_toolkit behaved like it does in GNU readline.  \r\n\r\nI've opened https://github.com/jonathanslenders/python-prompt-toolkit/issues/431 to move the discussion over there."
